#originalStanceText=No
#originalTopic=does-intelligent-design-have-merit
Science is about how things work. The stories, myths and legends of our origins aren't about explaining how creation was accomplished. They are about explaining basic human needs and emotions - and about how man fits with both nature and himself. Like much great art, they can tell a truth without representing fact. People taking them literally miss the authors' intent. 